                                                    S. <bibl><ref target="#http://opac.sub.uni-goettingen.de/DB=1/PPNSET?PPN=31731727X"><emph>Lettres from a painter II.</emph> 135.</ref></bibl> die ganze Ope- <lb id="d25462e68441" n="21"/>
                                                    ration beshreibet Graf <bibl><ref target="#http://hdl.handle.net/2027/ucm.5319456911?urlappend=%3Bseq=629"><emph>Caylus. Mem: XXV. <lb id="d25462e68447" n="22"/>
                                                    p.</emph> 309</ref></bibl> Bey den alten war es auch shon <lb id="d25462e68451" n="23"/>
